        <div class="card-icon">📦</div>
        <h3>Bulk & Business</h3>
        <p>Regular shippers ke liye special rates aur business dashboard.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="card-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3>Insured Shipping</h3>
        <p>Valuable items ke liye full insurance. Pickup se delivery tak protected.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="card-icon">❄️</div>
        <h3>Fragile Care</h3>
        <p>Electronics aur breakable items ke liye special packaging & handling.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal">
        <div class="card-icon">↩️</div>
        <h3>Return Management</h3>
        <p>Easy reverse logistics. E-commerce returns ke liye ideal.</p>
