      <div class="step reveal"><div class="step-num">04</div><div class="step-icon">📍</div><h4>Live Track</h4><p>Real-time tracking. SMS + WhatsApp updates.</p></div>
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="step-num">05</div><div class="step-icon">✅</div><h4>Delivered</h4><p>Photo confirmation + signature proof.</p></div>
